data.description: Refreshed price! Immaculate MOON VALLEY home on 1/3 acre cul-de-sac lot. Wonderful floorplan will accommodate any lifestyle, with both formal and casual living spaces, large bedrooms and wood burning fireplace! Have kids and pets? Very private backyard with tons of outdoor space to run around in and explore, or just relax by the pool, grill some burgers and enjoy those mountain views! RV Gate, 3 car garage with workshop! Love to hike? Just steps from some of the best trails in Phoenix! VA assumable loan at 3.375%.
